text: Willem Molijn (20 July 1874 - 9 June 1957) was a Dutch fencer. He competed in the individual épée event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Dutch male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of the Netherlands Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Utrecht (city)
